LTTNG
=====

Ubuntu
=====
The LTTng PPA offers the latest stable versions of LTTng packages. To get packages from the PPA, follow these steps:
apt-add-repository ppa:lttng/ppa
apt-get update
apt-get install lttng-tools
apt-get install lttng-modules-dkms
apt-get install liblttng-ust-dev

- Installtion and buiding of lttng kernel modules (lttng-modules-dkms) using apt-get does not work on estuary Ubuntu platform. 
  Thus lttng module build from source code and installed into rootfs.
  
  The source code of lttng kernel module worked is lttng-modules-2.6.4.tar.bz2 (ubuntu version)
  downloaded from https://lttng.org/download/#build-from-source




